[
  {
    "startTime": 12.639,
    "endTime": 15.12,
    "text": "have you ever tried to understand a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.12,
    "endTime": 16.88,
    "text": "teenager"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.88,
    "endTime": 18.88,
    "text": "it's exhausting right"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.88,
    "endTime": 20.64,
    "text": "you must be puzzled by the fact that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.64,
    "endTime": 23.439,
    "text": "some teens do well in school"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.439,
    "endTime": 26.16,
    "text": "lead clubs and teams and volunteer in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.16,
    "endTime": 27.68,
    "text": "their communities"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.68,
    "endTime": 30.24,
    "text": "but they eat tide pods for an online"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.24,
    "endTime": 31.84,
    "text": "challenge"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.84,
    "endTime": 35.2,
    "text": "speed and text while driving binge drink"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.2,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "and experiment with illicit drugs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 40.96,
    "text": "how can so many teens be so smart"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.96,
    "endTime": 43.44,
    "text": "skilled and responsible"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.44,
    "endTime": 45.68,
    "text": "and careless risk takers at the same"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.68,
    "endTime": 46.96,
    "text": "time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.96,
    "endTime": 49.84,
    "text": "when i was 16 while frequently observing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.84,
    "endTime": 52.48,
    "text": "my peers in person as well as on social"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.48,
    "endTime": 53.6,
    "text": "media"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.6,
    "endTime": 56.079,
    "text": "i began to wonder why so many teens took"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.079,
    "endTime": 58.48,
    "text": "such crazy risks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.48,
    "endTime": 60.32,
    "text": "it seems like getting a certificate from"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.32,
    "endTime": 62.399,
    "text": "their class in the fifth grade"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.399,
    "endTime": 64.72,
    "text": "can't stop them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.72,
    "endTime": 66.479,
    "text": "what was even more alarming to me was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.479,
    "endTime": 68.4,
    "text": "that the more they exposed themselves to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.4,
    "endTime": 70.08,
    "text": "these harmful risks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.08,
    "endTime": 71.84,
    "text": "the easier it became for them to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.84,
    "endTime": 74.4,
    "text": "continue taking risks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.4,
    "endTime": 76.4,
    "text": "now this confused me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.4,
    "endTime": 80.08,
    "text": "but it also made me incredibly curious"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.08,
    "endTime": 82.159,
    "text": "so as someone with a name that literally"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.159,
    "endTime": 84.56,
    "text": "means to explore knowledge"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.56,
    "endTime": 86.32,
    "text": "i started searching for a scientific"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.32,
    "endTime": 88.4,
    "text": "explanation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.4,
    "endTime": 90.88,
    "text": "now it's no secret that teens ages 13 to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.88,
    "endTime": 93.28,
    "text": "18 are more prone to risk taking than"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.28,
    "endTime": 95.119,
    "text": "children or adults"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.119,
    "endTime": 98.24,
    "text": "but what makes them so daring"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.24,
    "endTime": 100.72,
    "text": "do they suddenly become reckless or is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.72,
    "endTime": 102.4,
    "text": "this just a natural phase that they're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.4,
    "endTime": 103.759,
    "text": "going through"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.759,
    "endTime": 105.36,
    "text": "well neuroscientists have already found"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.36,
    "endTime": 107.119,
    "text": "evidence that the teen brain is still in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.119,
    "endTime": 109.52,
    "text": "the process of maturation and that this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.52,
    "endTime": 111.2,
    "text": "makes them exceptionally poor at"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.2,
    "endTime": 112.64,
    "text": "decision making"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.64,
    "endTime": 114.399,
    "text": "causing them to fall prey to risky"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.399,
    "endTime": 116.079,
    "text": "behaviors"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.079,
    "endTime": 118.32,
    "text": "but in that case if the maturing brain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.32,
    "endTime": 119.52,
    "text": "is to blame"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.52,
    "endTime": 121.36,
    "text": "then why are teens more vulnerable than"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.36,
    "endTime": 123.2,
    "text": "children even though their brains are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.2,
    "endTime": 125.439,
    "text": "more developed than those of children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.439,
    "endTime": 127.439,
    "text": "also not all teens in the world take"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.439,
    "endTime": 129.36,
    "text": "risks at the same level"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.36,
    "endTime": 131.36,
    "text": "are there some other underlying or"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.36,
    "endTime": 133.599,
    "text": "unintentional causes driving them to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.599,
    "endTime": 135.28,
    "text": "risk-taking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.28,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "well this is exactly what i decided to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 139.84,
    "text": "research"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.84,
    "endTime": 142.0,
    "text": "so i founded my research on the basis of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.0,
    "endTime": 143.92,
    "text": "a psychological process known as"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.92,
    "endTime": 145.36,
    "text": "habituation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.36,
    "endTime": 147.84,
    "text": "or simply what we refer to as getting"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.84,
    "endTime": 149.28,
    "text": "used to it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.28,
    "endTime": 151.44,
    "text": "habituation explains how our brains"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.44,
    "endTime": 154.4,
    "text": "adapt to some behaviors like lying with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.4,
    "endTime": 157.2,
    "text": "repeated exposures and this concept"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.2,
    "endTime": 158.8,
    "text": "inspired me to design a project to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.8,
    "endTime": 161.04,
    "text": "determine if the same principle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.04,
    "endTime": 162.959,
    "text": "could be applied to the relentless rise"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.959,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "of risk taking in teenagers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 167.519,
    "text": "so i predicted that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.519,
    "endTime": 169.76,
    "text": "habituation to risk taking may have the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.76,
    "endTime": 171.599,
    "text": "potential to change the already"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.599,
    "endTime": 174.48,
    "text": "vulnerable teenage brain by blunting or"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.48,
    "endTime": 176.48,
    "text": "even eradicating the negative emotions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.48,
    "endTime": 178.16,
