  {
    "startTime": 249.519,
    "endTime": 252.159,
    "text": "i was also a stubborn teenager"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.159,
    "endTime": 254.08,
    "text": "and as the daughter of bangladeshi"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.08,
    "endTime": 255.84,
    "text": "immigrants and one of just a handful of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.84,
