    "endTime": 269.52,
    "text": "brown girl who was an anomaly in my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.52,
    "endTime": 271.68,
    "text": "homogenous hometown"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.68,
    "endTime": 273.52,
    "text": "i hope that by doing this research i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.52,
    "endTime": 276.16,
    "text": "could establish this and how valuable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.16,
    "endTime": 278.32,
